OL,3,C'I felt as though it was my fault':
OL,4,CJayesh Khunti's victims speak out over
OL,5,Cabuse
OL,7,FThe names of the victims have been
OL,8,Fchanged to protect their identities.
OL,10,FAs Jayesh Khunti is sentenced to 13
OL,11,Fyears for multiple historic sexual
OL,12,Fabuse offences in Loughborough, two of
OL,13,Fhis victims have told ITV News Central
OL,14,Fabout the impact the abuse has had on
OL,15,Fthem.
OL,17,FHe was found guilty at Leicester Crown
OL,18,FCourt of 16 counts of sexual abuse
OL,19,Fagainst five children going back more
OL,20,Fthan 40 years.
