OL,3,C'I felt as though it was my fault':
OL,4,CJayesh Khunti's victims speak out over
OL,5,Cabuse
OL,7,FKhunti, who is now in his 50s, began
OL,8,Fabusing his victims when he was a
OL,9,Fteenager.
OL,11,FFor "Mahesh", the abuse started in the
OL,12,F1980s when he was just four and
OL,13,Fcontinued until he was nine, although
OL,14,Fhe didn't tell anyone until three
OL,15,Fyears ago.
OL,17,F"I remember I woke up in the middle of
OL,18,Fthe night with flashbacks of being
OL,19,Fsexually abused, remembering all the
OL,20,Fmost awful stuff that could've
OL,21,Fhappened happened," he said.
