OL,3,C'I felt as though it was my fault':
OL,4,CJayesh Khunti's victims speak out over
OL,5,Cabuse
OL,7,F"Within three or four days, I found
OL,8,Fthe other four victims and told them I
OL,9,Fwas going to report it. Within a few
OL,10,Fweeks of that, I reported it to the
OL,11,Fpolice."
OL,13,F"Mahesh" began counselling with a
OL,14,Ftherapist after a friend suggested his
OL,15,Fsevere back pain and food allergies
OL,16,Fcould be linked to emotional trauma.
OL,18,FAnother victim, "Hena", was five at
OL,19,Fthe time, and endured unimaginable
OL,20,Ftorment for four years.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/10
