OL,3,C'I felt as though it was my fault':
OL,4,CJayesh Khunti's victims speak out over
OL,5,Cabuse
OL,7,F"It made me feel as though it was my
OL,8,Ffault... (as though) I deserved that.
OL,9,FI had no one to turn to. I couldn't
OL,10,Ftell anyone, I thought no one would
OL,11,Fbelieve me," she said.
OL,13,F"Also, the men in our family were put
OL,14,Fon a pedestal. They could do no wrong,
OL,15,Fso I didn't think I stood a chance.
OL,17,F"I was adamant about coming forward
OL,18,Fand I just hope that if this has
OL,19,Fhappened to anybody else, it will give
OL,20,Fthem the courage to speak up and get
OL,21,Fjustice.
