OL,3,C'I felt as though it was my fault':
OL,4,CJayesh Khunti's victims speak out over
OL,5,Cabuse
OL,7,F"It's a deterrent for people who are
OL,8,Fthinking about abusing children."
OL,10,F"Hena" said she found it difficult to
OL,11,Fspeak out but knew it could help other
OL,12,Fpeople.
OL,14,F"I always felt as though this person
OL,15,Fshould be protected... (but) why am I
OL,16,Fprotecting this person? Because it
OL,17,Fcould be happening to other people,"
OL,18,Fshe said.
