OL,3,C'I felt as though it was my fault':
OL,4,CJayesh Khunti's victims speak out over
OL,5,Cabuse
OL,7,F'I felt it was quite important to
OL,8,Fbreak that cycle... I felt it was
OL,9,Fsomething I needed to do for myself
OL,10,Fand also for others because it could
OL,11,Fbe happening now to someone else,
OL,12,Fanother child, another innocent
OL,13,Fperson."
OL,15,FBoth "Mahesh" and "Hena" said they
OL,16,Ffelt there was a stigma surrounding
OL,17,Fabuse within the Asian community,
OL,18,Fmeaning many victims often suffer in
OL,19,Fsilence.
