OL,3,C'I felt as though it was my fault':
OL,4,CJayesh Khunti's victims speak out over
OL,5,Cabuse
OL,7,F"Hena" said: "Being in the Asian
OL,8,Fcommunity, you respect your elders and
OL,9,Fwhen you've got an elder, you just
OL,10,Fobey, because that's what we've been
OL,11,Ftaught to do.
OL,13,F"I think (sexual abuse) perhaps
OL,14,Fhappens quite a lot and and gets swept
OL,15,Funder the carpet. And I think there
OL,16,Fare people who, due to family
OL,17,Fdynamics, just aren't able to speak
OL,18,Fout."
OL,20,F"Mahesh" said removing the stigma is
OL,21,Fessential.
