OL,3,C'I felt as though it was my fault':
OL,4,CJayesh Khunti's victims speak out over
OL,5,Cabuse
OL,7,F"You've got to educate children from
OL,8,Freally young about what's appropriate
OL,9,Fand what's inappropriate. Jayesh
OL,10,FKhunti had complete access to us.
OL,12,F"It's just about raising awareness for
OL,13,Fother victims and then hopefully we
OL,14,Fcan better protect other children as
OL,15,Fwell."
OL,17,FJayesh Khunti's reign of terror is
OL,18,Ffinally over, which is a huge sense of
OL,19,Frelief for his victims like "Mahesh"
OL,20,Fand "Hena".
