OL,3,C'I felt as though it was my fault':
OL,4,CJayesh Khunti's victims speak out over
OL,5,Cabuse
OL,7,F"Mahesh" said: "His actions were
OL,8,Fpretty evil... pretty awful. And he
OL,9,Fwas just very motivated to get what he
OL,10,Fwanted.
OL,12,F"I just hope he can get help and is
OL,13,Fable to find a way to be able to own
OL,14,Fup to what's happened. I don't wish
OL,15,Fill of him. We needed justice. I
OL,16,Fneeded to speak up for that little
OL,17,Fboy."
OL,19,F"Hena" said it has taken a lot of
OL,20,Fenergy to come to terms with what
OL,21,Fhappened and find a way to move on.
