OL,3,C'I felt as though it was my fault':
OL,4,CJayesh Khunti's victims speak out over
OL,5,Cabuse
OL,7,FShe said: "I was a child, there were
OL,8,Fparts of my childhood which were
OL,9,Fruined because of him. It shaped a lot
OL,10,Fof my future and I had to do a lot of
OL,11,Finner work to try and be who I am now.
OL,13,F"I felt worthless and that has taken a
OL,14,Flong time to rectify."
OL,16,F"Mahesh" and "Hena's" horrific ordeal
OL,17,Fis behind them and the path to
OL,18,Frecovery is long and winding. But it
OL,19,Fwill be a journey of healing where
OL,20,Fthey hope to inspire others to seek
OL,21,Fhelp.
